text: Arthur Nichols (3 September 1881 - 19 November 1937) was an Australian cricketer. He played two first-class matches for New South Wales in 1908/09. ==See also== * List of New South Wales representative cricketers ==References== ==External links== * Category:1881 births Category:1937 deaths Category:Australian cricketers Category:New South Wales cricketers Category:Cricketers from Sydney
title: Arthur Nichols (cricketer)
